  "text": "Self-control was assessed with the Dutch translation of the Self-Control Scale [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . This scale consisted of 11 items (e.g., \"I am good at resisting temptation\"; \"I am able to work effectively toward long-term goals\"; 1 ¼ completely disagree, 5 ¼ completely agree) and showed acceptable internal reliability (as ¼ .72-.78 across waves).",
